articles.title: ICC World Cup 2023: 'It hurts', says Buttler as champions England crash out - Moneycontrol
articles.description: Australia had been bowled out for 286 but still had enough firepower to dismiss England for 253 as the defending champions remain bottom of the table and still with two games to play.
articles.content:
England skipper Jos Buttler admitted that "it hurts" to see his defending champions knocked out of the Cricket World Cup.
